1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 29 =

20
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:46,740
I think Chief Xia is truly mad about you.

21
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,180
He spoils that concubine,

22
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,140
only because he still likes you.

23
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,500
The Partridge Sky he wrote

24
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,020
is deeply touching.

25
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,420
Many people in the palace

26
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:01,460
are making private copies.

27
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:04,140
He used to be

28
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,700
a prudent and slick man.

29
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,220
His wife pushed him.

30
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:16,180
It was my fault.

31
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,460
I found a maid who looked

32
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:25,540
somewhat alike the young me,

33
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,900
and sent her to the Xia Mansion after instruction.

34
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,100
I had planned

35
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,700
to drive his wife crazy

36
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:38,500
so that Xia Song would no longer tolerate her.

37
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,580
But I didn’t expect his wife

38
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:43,380
to be so insane!

39
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,660
She made him a laughing stock.

40
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:52,020
Even His Majesty knew it.

41
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:55,140
Don’t worry, aunt.

42
00:02:56,300 --> 00:02:57,700
I will put in a good word for him

43
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:58,980
in front of His Majesty.

44
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:01,100
No.

45
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:03,620
Don’t do that.

46
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:05,780
Chief Li of Styling, she...

47
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,100
His Majesty won’t treat me like that.

48
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:09,740
I know. I know.

49
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,020
But...

50
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:13,020
Why must you annoy His Majesty?

51
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:14,620
Besides,

52
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:16,900
it won’t help him.

53
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:19,660
What do we do then?

54
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:22,300
We can’t just watch and do nothing.

55
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:24,340
His Majesty has arrived.

56
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:30,980
Qiuhe.

57
00:03:31,180 --> 00:03:32,260
What kind of jewel

58
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:34,020
do you think

59
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:36,140
shall be used for my crown?

60
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,500
What about jade?

61
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:42,460
= Dong Qiuhe =
Please think carefully about it.

62
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:45,220
Don’t try to buy expensive jewels.

63
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,820
Stand up and talk.

64
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:50,100
In the Capital,

65
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:52,220
rich families and civilians

66
00:03:52,620 --> 00:03:54,820
regard what madams in the palace want as a fashion.

67
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:57,700
Whenever they know what madams buy,

68
00:03:57,820 --> 00:03:58,860
they also buy it.

69
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:00,460
The prices rocket then.

70
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:01,860
For example,

71
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:04,180
Madam Zhang likes Jiangxi kumquat.

72
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,780
Since people knew that,

73
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:08,220
the price of kumquat has hiked.

74
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,580
When I went out for business,

75
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:13,220
I found the price of half-kilo Jiangxi kumquat

76
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,340
was as high as four-kilo mutton.

77
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:18,580
Good gracious!

78
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:21,420
Madam, please don’t buy expensive jewels.

79
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:26,420
Good girl.

80
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:27,460
Stand up.

81
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:31,100
It’s so considerate of you.

82
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:33,660
In order not to

83
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:35,300
be defeated by Madam Zhang,

84
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,660
I’ve even lost my mind.

85
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,420
What she said

86
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,060
reminds me of something.

87
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:43,180
Several days ago,

88
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,740
His Majesty told the Bureau of Clothing that

89
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:46,900
his informal robes didn’t need to have

90
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:49,140
complicated tapestry patterns.

91
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:50,860
Such luxurious clothes

92
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:53,540
will cost a year’s expense of

93
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:54,740
a well-to-do family.

94
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:57,420
His Majesty is always generous to us.

95
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:59,020
But if he knows

96
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,900
we spend much money on jewels

97
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:02,940
just for vanity,

98
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,580
he will be annoyed.

99
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,180
I don’t think

100
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:10,220
you need to worry

101
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:11,380
if Madam Zhang will steal the show

102
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:13,100
on jewels.

103
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,340
Speaking of jewels,

104
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:17,780
she always has the best.

105
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,500
You don’t need to compete.

106
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:22,060
You mean

107
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:25,140
I’m overestimating myself?

108
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:27,700
Not really.

109
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:30,140
What do you mean then?

110
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,700
On the seventh day of July,

111
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,620
His Majesty will choose the best maid

112
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:35,900
to comb the hair of him.

113
00:05:36,820 --> 00:05:39,140
He has a different hair style from madams.

114
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:41,300
No flowery crown is required.

115
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,340
As far as I see,

116
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,660
by then we only need to

117
00:05:45,660 --> 00:05:46,820
comb your hair well.

118
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:50,340
The crown is only ornament.

119
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:53,220
We can use some silk flowers,

120
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:56,900
and even fresh flowers.

121
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,340
If we use a priceless crown,

122
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,340
it will be a reversal.

123
00:06:02,940 --> 00:06:03,820
Good girl.

124
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:06,260
You’re young, but clever.

125
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:07,940
Thank you for reminding me,

126
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:09,340
and it saves trouble.

127
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:10,860
You know.

128
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:12,860
I also recommend a maid to His Majesty.

129
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,940
You said this in front of me.

130
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:18,420
It means you really are big-hearted.

131
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:20,340
If this girl

132
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:22,420
can serve His Majesty,

133
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,660
it’ll be our luck.

134
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:29,060
I like Qiuhe, too.

135
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:32,980
When father talks with officials,

136
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,740
Huaiji accompanies him.

137
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:38,220
If Qiuhe can take care of father

138
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,940
in the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility,

139
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:43,420
I will be relieved.

140
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:45,540
Look at her.

141
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,940
Sounds like she takes care of his father,

142
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:50,580
instead of he taking care of you.

143
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:53,460
Since father was sick,

144
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:55,180
he hasn’t completely recovered.

145
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:58,180
I saw him press over his heart several times.

146
00:06:58,660 --> 00:07:01,060
He doesn’t want to blame his maids.

147
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:03,700
When his maid is careless,

148
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:06,460
father will suffer more.

149
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:07,940
I only want the best maid

150
00:07:07,940 --> 00:07:10,340
to take care of father.

151
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,180
You’re right, Huirou.

152
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:15,420
Your father is benevolent.

153
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:17,020
He never blames any maid

154
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,300
for his own business.

155
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,260
I neglected that, too.

156
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,300
Huirou, you care for you father most.

157
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:25,060
And he spoils you.

158
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:29,100
- Thank you, Princess. - Thank you, Princess.

159
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:30,340
- You flatter me. - You flatter me.

160
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:32,620
- I’ll do my duty. - I’ll do our duty.

161
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:35,380
When you stay together,

162
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:38,700
you look more like a couple

163
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:40,500
than Zongshi and Taotao.

164
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,940
Don’t talk nonsense.

165
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,540
Mmm, I see.

166
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:49,700
Zongshi and Taotao are

167
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,180
royal relatives.

168
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:53,260
I can’t compare you to them.

169
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:56,540
But no one tells them.

170
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,220
Let’s go.

171
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,940
They’ll comb their hair.

172
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,420
And let’s go painting.

173
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:06,500
Huaiji, you met me before anyone else.

174
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:07,580
So,

175
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:10,660
however close you get to other girls,

176
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,140
or whatever couple you make with them,

177
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,940
you must like me most.

178
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:23,660
Your Majesty.

179
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,140
Whatever problem Chief Xia has

180
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,300
with his wife,

181
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:29,900
it has nothing to do with my aunt.

182
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,780
Her true heart

183
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:34,660
has been burnt to ashes.

184
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:37,540
Must she be blamed

185
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,260
only because his wife

186
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:41,300
is jealous of his concubine?

187
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:46,380
Why is she to be blamed?

188
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:49,420
For they grew up together

189
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,740
and were engaged under the order of parents,

190
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:54,180
but the late Emperor broke them up?

191
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,580
Chief Xia couldn’t forget my aunt

192
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:58,340
and found a substitute.

193
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:01,060
He’s now quarreling with his wife

194
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,300
and disgracing the imperial court.

195
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:03,020
Watch your tongue!

196
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:05,220
The late Emperor didn’t know.

197
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:07,180
But now you know. So what?

198
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,380
Anyway, you always

199
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:11,460
care for the legal wife.

200
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,540
I’m overstepping my authority again.

201
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:17,140
Why don’t you

202
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,020
just kick us out?

203
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,660
People will be cheering.

204
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:22,700
No!

205
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:23,780
Don’t say that, madam.

206
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:25,500
Your Majesty.

207
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:27,500
Don’t blame her for indiscreet remarks.

208
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:28,900
A pregnant lady is always testy.

209
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:29,660
All right.

210
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:32,380
I didn’t say I would blame someone.

211
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:35,460
It’s not your fault, anyway.

212
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:36,980
I just want to confirm

213
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:38,500
what Xia Song told me.

214
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:42,180
Your Majesty,

215
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:44,060
do you also think she’s innocent?

216
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:48,900
Don’t be angry, Your Majesty.

217
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:51,020
I’m just afraid that

218
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:51,820
people in and out of the palace

219
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:52,780
are mocking me

220
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:53,700
for this.

221
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:55,500
I’m afraid

222
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:57,060
you might punish all of them

223
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:57,980
without a reason.

224
00:09:58,820 --> 00:09:59,860
Good point.

225
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,380
So, in your heart,

226
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:02,780
I’m so confused that

227
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,620
I will punish innocent people when I’m angry

228
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:05,780
without a reason?

229
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:07,900
No. No. No.

230
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:10,340
You’re the most sensible man.

231
00:10:10,340 --> 00:10:11,620
You’re never confused.

232
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,100
It’s my fault.

233
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:14,180
I’ll slap myself.

234
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:15,700
All right.

235
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:17,900
Look at you.

236
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,100
You cry and laugh.

237
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:20,900
Go.

238
00:10:21,380 --> 00:10:22,380
Get in

239
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,340
and wash your face.

240
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:45,820
The late Emperor didn’t know Xia Song was engaged.

241
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:49,020
He gave Xia Song a wife and promoted him

242
00:10:49,020 --> 00:10:50,300
after his father died,

243
00:10:51,780 --> 00:10:53,420
as compensation for his family.

244
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:55,980
Unexpectedly, all of you were hurt.

245
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:58,500
Xia Song and his wife hate each other for decades.

246
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:01,300
And you’ve been all alone.

247
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,580
The late Emperor cared a lot

248
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:10,220
for his subordinate.

249
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,060
I never complained about that.

250
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,380
It’s my fate.

251
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,420
I don’t dare to complain.

252
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:29,300
What’s done is done.

253
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:31,540
I asked Xia Song

254
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,860
what had exactly happened.

255
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,740
Instead of hiding,

256
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:35,620
he told me everything.

257
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:37,900
He also said

258
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:40,860
he deliberately uncovered his feelings

259
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,780
so that everyone in the world could know

260
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:45,260
he was forced

261
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:46,140
ever since his wedding day

262
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,900
and he loved someone else.

263
00:11:49,940 --> 00:11:51,980
He had wanted to force his wife to divorce

264
00:11:52,380 --> 00:11:53,900
and to let you know his love for you.

265
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:55,380
After that,

266
00:11:56,900 --> 00:11:58,180
he would like to be expelled

267
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:01,340
to wherever desolate as I wish.

268
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:04,860
His wife, however,

269
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:06,580
didn’t ask for divorce.

270
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:08,380
Instead, she wrote a letter of confession

271
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:09,660
in all tears

272
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:10,740
and gave it to the Empress.

273
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:14,860
She said she was jealous

274
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:15,860
and it was all her fault.

275
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:17,540
She would take all the blame.

276
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:18,620
She didn’t fear to be killed,

277
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:22,700
but she must be buried in Xia’s ancestral hall.

278
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:26,500
I think

279
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:29,060
if it goes on,

280
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,180
they’ll be more disgraced.

281
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:34,620
Since it was caused

282
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:36,020
by my father’s marriage edict,

283
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:37,300
I will

284
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,980
end it today

285
00:12:41,180 --> 00:12:42,180
with a divorce edict.

286
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:50,700
Yet decades have passed.

287
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,700
You both are no longer young.

288
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:56,260
I won’t let him marry you.

289
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:58,300
If he married you,

290
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:02,140
his wife would be more rancorous.

291
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:06,380
Her family would be more disgraced, too.

292
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:11,860
Your Majesty.

293
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:21,540
It’s so kind of you, Your Majesty.

294
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,020
It’s...

295
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,380
It’s my luck.

296
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:27,940
I’ve never expected.

297
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,140
I’m already working here.

298
00:13:32,460 --> 00:13:33,580
I don’t dream to

299
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:35,420
be with him again.

300
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:38,380
All I want

301
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:40,740
is to stay with Madam Zhang

302
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:43,420
and take care of her baby.

303
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:46,740
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

304
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,740
Since you let them divorce,

305
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:54,340
I will

306
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:58,060
no longer think of him.

307
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:00,820
I will

308
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:05,540
never try to contact him.

309
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:12,980
I used to

310
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:17,020
dislike you.

311
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:20,860
But what Xia Song told me today

312
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:22,500
made me sigh.

313
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:26,980
You truly care for Bihan.

314
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:29,620
She didn’t mistrust you

315
00:14:29,900 --> 00:14:31,620
because she was naive.

316
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:37,500
Whatever happened in the past

317
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:40,100
is over today.

318
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:41,580
Don’t think about it again

319
00:14:42,420 --> 00:14:43,900
whether you’re convinced or not.

320
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:48,060
Bihan treats you as her mother.

321
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:49,340
She’s sincere to you

322
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:50,340
and she trusts you.

323
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:53,940
If you behave yourself

324
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:56,060
and take good care of her and her baby,

325
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,660
I won’t be mean to you.

326
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:00,220
If you don’t behave yourself,

327
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,620
collude with others for trouble,

328
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:03,860
or incite my concubine,

329
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:07,420
I won’t spare your life.

330
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,060
Thank you, Your Majesty.

331
00:15:16,460 --> 00:15:17,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

332
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:30,420
Huaiji.

333
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,300
Mr. Cui taught you to paint

334
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:33,580
for days.

335
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,060
Come and have a look.

336
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:40,100
Her Highness?

337
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,340
Really?

338
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:45,340
Sorry, I’m too stupid to guess.

339
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:47,900
But this headwear

340
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:49,580
is different from what she usually wears.

341
00:15:54,260 --> 00:15:55,980
I’ve never learnt to paint.

342
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,060
But I liked to paint since I was little.

343
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,580
Sometime,

344
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,740
when I miss someone

345
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:03,100
or worry about something,

346
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:05,700
I couldn’t help painting casually.

347
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:10,900
This painting

348
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:12,940
is too ugly to show others.

349
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,100
When it’s dry,

350
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,100
put it away for me.

351
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:18,700
I remember you can mount paintings.

352
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:20,300
When I was little,

353
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:22,020
I helped at my uncle’s shop.

354
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:24,780
But I was too young

355
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:25,740
to mount it well.

356
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:27,260
It’s okay.

357
00:16:28,140 --> 00:16:29,380
Regardless of my identity,

358
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:33,020
this is just a child’s poor painting.

359
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:34,940
Oh,

360
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:35,820
I’ve got another painting.

361
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,700
Mount it, too.

362
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:38,980
In the third drawer of

363
00:16:39,220 --> 00:16:40,460
the second row on the right,

364
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:41,340
there’s a wooden box.

365
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:42,260
Go fetch it.

366
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:19,420
Huaiji.

367
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,340
Do you like Her Highness?

368
00:17:24,660 --> 00:17:25,580
Her Highness is...

369
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,100
Stop.

370
00:17:28,580 --> 00:17:29,620
Don’t try to tell me

371
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:32,180
her virtues or good deeds.

372
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,220
I’m just asking.

373
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:36,220
Do you like her?

374
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,420
I don’t know.

375
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:41,100
You don’t know?

376
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:44,100
I respect her.

377
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:50,860
Respect?

378
00:17:56,580 --> 00:17:57,420
Respect.

379
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:06,100
You know what? It’s the best way.

380
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:17,220
Madam.

381
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:18,260
Her Highness

382
00:18:18,260 --> 00:18:19,420
picked out the girl for us.

383
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:20,460
She said the girl is

384
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:22,700
only two years older than Princess Huirou.

385
00:18:22,980 --> 00:18:24,300
She doesn’t work too much now.

386
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:26,220
She can just play with the Princess.

387
00:18:27,700 --> 00:18:28,900
How long have you been in the palace?

388
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,500
Who did you work for?

389
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:31,900
Almost one year.

390
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:33,900
My aunt is Miss Chen of Bureau of Food.

391
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:35,540
She took me here.

392
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:40,860
Well, you shall stay in my place.

393
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,260
You’re a little girl.

394
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:43,860
Ask if you have any confusion.

395
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:45,940
If you want something,

396
00:18:46,100 --> 00:18:47,220
ask Lusi for it.

397
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:51,300
Take her to play with Huirou.

398
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,100
Madam.

399
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:03,540
Huaiji comes to paint with Princess.

400
00:19:04,380 --> 00:19:05,260
Get him in.

401
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:12,500
I got up one hour later today.

402
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:13,660
Sorry to keep you waiting.

403
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:16,740
Didn’t go to the Hall of Politics with His Majesty?

404
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:18,900
Elder Princess is ill.

405
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:20,380
His Majesty has gone to visit her.

406
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,300
Mr. Zhang went with him.

407
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:24,740
His Majesty asked me to paint with Princess.

408
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:27,100
She painted magpies last time.

409
00:19:27,460 --> 00:19:28,980
His Majesty liked that.

410
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,700
Mr. Cui also said she painted vivid magpies

411
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,060
with much progress.

412
00:19:33,700 --> 00:19:36,220
His Majesty then asked her

413
00:19:36,460 --> 00:19:37,300
to learn more diligently.

414
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:40,180
He’ll come and see her paint someday.

415
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:43,020
Oh, he really wants Huirou

416
00:19:43,060 --> 00:19:44,260
to be a female painter.

417
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:48,380
Anyway, I don’t understand painting.

418
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,620
I’ll leave her to you.

419
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:54,620
She will be your maid, Princess.

420
00:19:55,060 --> 00:19:57,180
Why don’t you give her a name?

421
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,660
What’s your family name?

422
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:00,860
Jiang.

423
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:03,260
Jiang?

424
00:20:07,620 --> 00:20:08,380
Oh, I know.

425
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:10,460
I’ll call you Spicy Ginger.

426
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:12,060
Spicy...

427
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:13,420
Spicy Ginger?

428
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,820
Think about it, Princess.

429
00:20:17,540 --> 00:20:18,860
With such a name,

430
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:21,740
people will laugh at her.

431
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:25,340
Isn’t it a good name?

432
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:27,900
I have spicy ginger for every breakfast.

433
00:20:29,180 --> 00:20:30,700
Why don’t you think of a better one?

434
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:32,860
Well, I’ll think about it.

435
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:45,500
Taste it, Princess.

436
00:20:47,020 --> 00:20:48,180
Today is an even-numbered day

437
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:49,500
and we have candied fruits!

438
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:50,660
Come over.

439
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:55,420
They’re made of plums from Jiaqing Yard,

440
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,060
also known as Jiaqing Zi.

441
00:20:57,060 --> 00:20:58,420
I love them most.

442
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:01,220
I can only have some on every even-numbered day.

443
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:02,460
Come.

444
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,460
Give me your hands.

445
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:11,540
This is for you.

446
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,740
Jiaqing Zi will be your name.

447
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:16,900
= Jiaqing Zi =

448
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:20,100
This is Xiangyuan Zi.

449
00:21:22,300 --> 00:21:25,100
This is Yun Guo’er.

450
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:28,700
And this is Xiao Ye’er.

451
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:32,260
We’ll play together.

452
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,260
Oh,

453
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:35,660
this is Huaiji.

454
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:38,300
He works for my father

455
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:39,420
and doesn’t live here.

456
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:41,820
But he’s my best friend.

457
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,020
Thanks to him.

458
00:21:44,380 --> 00:21:46,900
He showed me the candied fruits.

459
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:50,580
Or I would have named you

460
00:21:50,580 --> 00:21:52,500
Eel Bun.

461
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:59,180
Did you know Jia Yulan’s relationship

462
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:01,100
with Xia Song

463
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:02,500
before she returned to the palace

464
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:03,660
and took care of Madam Zhang?

465
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:06,180
Yes, I knew.

466
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:09,220
Because of that poem,

467
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:10,940
some scholars knew

468
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:13,180
what happened to Xia Song that year.

469
00:22:14,460 --> 00:22:15,860
It was a private affair

470
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:18,940
and he got married because of the late Emperor.

471
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:21,300
No one told you about it.

472
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:23,460
I almost heard about it,

473
00:22:23,860 --> 00:22:26,300
in 1038 A.D.

474
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:27,700
I confirmed it several days later

475
00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:29,260
and recorded it

476
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:31,380
in the Secret Book of Imperial Security Agency.

477
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,740
Public and private affairs,

478
00:22:36,060 --> 00:22:37,140
big or small,

479
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:39,380
that people talk about,

480
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:42,780
is there anything you don’t know?

481
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:46,420
In the Imperial Security Agency,

482
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:48,980
my job is to collect
as much information as possible.

483
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:51,140
I don’t dare to say I know everything.

484
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,140
You’re busy, Your Majesty.

485
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:55,380
I must pick out important things

486
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:56,580
for your instruction.

487
00:22:58,180 --> 00:23:00,780
Sometimes, I make a wrong judgement, too.

488
00:23:12,900 --> 00:23:13,700
Your Majesty!

489
00:23:30,060 --> 00:23:31,020
Huaiji.

490
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:32,300
You’re amazing.

491
00:23:32,660 --> 00:23:34,500
You helped a little.

492
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:36,420
And the duck becomes vivid.

493
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:39,180
This is the best duck I’ve ever painted.

494
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,220
You flatter me, Princess.

495
00:23:43,140 --> 00:23:44,420
Because His Majesty

496
00:23:44,420 --> 00:23:45,580
loves you,

497
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:47,980
I’ve got the luck

498
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:49,260
to learn from Mr. Cui.

499
00:23:50,340 --> 00:23:51,820
It’s so clever of you.

500
00:23:52,260 --> 00:23:54,540
You’ll be an amazing painter

501
00:23:54,780 --> 00:23:56,820
just like Mr. Cui.

502
00:23:57,780 --> 00:24:00,020
Then I can tell others that

503
00:24:00,180 --> 00:24:01,500
when I was little,

504
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:02,860
Mr. Liang once

505
00:24:02,980 --> 00:24:04,780
held my hand

506
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,700
and painted the eyes of the duck.

507
00:24:07,860 --> 00:24:09,740
Mr. Cui is a born genius.

508
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:12,780
Even if someone else learns from him,

509
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:14,420
he can’t be as good,

510
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:16,780
however hard he tries.

511
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:18,980
I’m a philistine.

512
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:21,260
I only work as a messenger.

513
00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:23,140
Huaiji.

514
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:24,180
I don’t like it

515
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:26,180
when you think you’re a philistine.

516
00:24:26,300 --> 00:24:28,220
I think you’re amazing

517
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:29,700
and clever.

518
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:32,300
Father thinks you’re good, too.

519
00:24:32,580 --> 00:24:34,380
If you still say you’re a philistine,

520
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:35,900
you mean I’m too stupid

521
00:24:36,260 --> 00:24:37,580
to judge people.

522
00:24:38,900 --> 00:24:39,940
That’s disrespecting me.

523
00:24:44,860 --> 00:24:46,700
Thank you for your appreciation.

524
00:24:48,580 --> 00:24:49,660
I’ll have a little secret

525
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:50,780
with you.

526
00:24:52,980 --> 00:24:56,060
When no one else is around,

527
00:24:56,060 --> 00:24:58,380
you don’t need kneel or kowtow.

528
00:24:59,060 --> 00:24:59,860
I...

529
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:02,020
But no, Princess.

530
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:04,540
Sometimes, father doesn’t ask some officials

531
00:25:04,540 --> 00:25:07,140
to kneel or kowtow.

532
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:09,940
Father says they don’t need to kowtow

533
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:12,420
in case of private discussion.

534
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:14,220
When father is here,

535
00:25:14,900 --> 00:25:16,300
and no one else is around,

536
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:19,180
he doesn’t ask my mother to kneel, either.

537
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:21,740
How can I compare myself to

538
00:25:22,060 --> 00:25:23,220
officials or Concubine Miao?

539
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:25,060
You can take the imperial exam,

540
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,980
and be an official, too.

541
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,740
Father said no family background was needed

542
00:25:29,060 --> 00:25:30,900
for the imperial exam.

543
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:32,380
Whoever is clever and works hard

544
00:25:32,780 --> 00:25:34,940
can serve the country.

545
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:38,180
I recited grandpa’s poem.

546
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:41,700
Don’t hate it when no one serves you.

547
00:25:43,380 --> 00:25:46,500
In books, there are many servants.

548
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:49,340
Don’t hate it when you don’t have a good wife.

549
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:52,420
In books, there is a house of beautiful girls.

550
00:25:53,100 --> 00:25:55,660
When a man has ambitions,

551
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:59,620
he must study hard.

552
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:04,500
Princess.

553
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:07,300
Eunuchs like me

554
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:10,500
can’t leave the palace unless we die.

555
00:26:11,340 --> 00:26:12,620
We don’t get married,

556
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:14,660
or take the imperial exam.

557
00:26:14,940 --> 00:26:16,460
We can never be officials.

558
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:18,900
Why?

559
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:24,740
This is a rule.

560
00:26:30,860 --> 00:26:31,620
Princess.

561
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:33,300
Here come Miss Zhou and Miss Fan.

562
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:35,180
Be right there.

563
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:42,820
Huaiji, don’t be sad.

564
00:26:43,820 --> 00:26:46,020
It doesn’t matter

565
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:47,260
when you can’t be an official.

566
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:49,060
Look at those officials.

567
00:26:49,220 --> 00:26:49,940
They don’t stay with my father

568
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:51,740
as long as you do.

569
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:54,020
You stay with him every day.

570
00:26:54,100 --> 00:26:55,700
Even I’m jealous.

571
00:27:34,980 --> 00:27:35,780
Your Majesty.

572
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,020
My hair is in a mess.

573
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:40,180
Maoze.

574
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:42,220
Comb my hair.

575
00:27:44,660 --> 00:27:45,380
Aye.

576
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:01,980
Turn around. Turn! Turn!

577
00:28:02,020 --> 00:28:03,860
Don’t stop! Don’t stop!

578
00:28:08,700 --> 00:28:09,700
Madam Miao.

579
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:11,540
I’ve cleaned up

580
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:13,140
Princess’s painting room in the side hall.

581
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:15,260
I’ll take the painting back.

582
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,500
As His Majesty is tired with work at night,

583
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:19,420
I’ll show him this painting to refresh him.

584
00:28:20,460 --> 00:28:21,420
Good boy.

585
00:28:21,740 --> 00:28:22,900
It’s so considerate of you.

586
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:26,540
Qiuhe made me

587
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:28,020
a bun without a crown.

588
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,820
Looks simple and neat.

589
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:36,060
But this hair style is inconspicuous.

590
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:39,020
His Majesty is coming for dinner.

591
00:28:39,100 --> 00:28:40,340
Will he like it?

592
00:28:41,820 --> 00:28:42,580
Huaiji.

593
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,620
You’re a boy.

594
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:44,500
Why don’t you have a look?

595
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:48,220
I’ve never seen such a hairstyle before.

596
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:50,340
His Majesty

597
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:51,380
will be curious

598
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:52,660
and take a few more looks.

599
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:55,700
Looked carefully, the hairstyle is simple.

600
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:58,020
It doesn’t cover

601
00:28:58,180 --> 00:28:59,100
your own elegance

602
00:28:59,420 --> 00:29:00,820
with exquisite buns

603
00:29:01,100 --> 00:29:02,500
or expensive crowns.

604
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:04,420
I think

605
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:05,620
His Majesty will like it.

606
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,940
I like this hairstyle, too.

607
00:29:12,700 --> 00:29:13,780
But...

608
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,980
let me tell the truth.

609
00:29:18,460 --> 00:29:19,780
The seventh day of July is coming.

610
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,340
All madams

611
00:29:21,340 --> 00:29:23,180
who recommend the Combing Stewardess

612
00:29:23,300 --> 00:29:24,620
will never let go of any chance

613
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:26,140
to meet His Majesty.

614
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:29,740
We compete against each other

615
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:31,060
so that His Majesty can see

616
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:32,860
what our maids can do.

617
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:34,380
With this hairstyle,

618
00:29:34,580 --> 00:29:36,020
I look a bit more elegant

619
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:37,020
than I usually do.

620
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:39,660
But the hairstyle itself

621
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,260
isn’t very splendid.

622
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:43,740
Without a crown,

623
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:46,180
I’m afraid His Majesty will think

624
00:29:46,540 --> 00:29:49,260
this is the best Qiuhe can do.

625
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,380
I think

626
00:29:51,500 --> 00:29:54,300
His Majesty wants the best Combing Stewardess,

627
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:56,820
instead of the best crown maker.

628
00:29:57,700 --> 00:30:00,220
You don’t need to work on crowns.

629
00:30:01,300 --> 00:30:02,460
His Majesty doesn’t

630
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:04,300
want complicated hairstyles, either.

631
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:07,420
He wants comfortable and careful work.

632
00:30:10,780 --> 00:30:11,540
Fine, then.

633
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,740
Let it be.

634
00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:16,060
But without a crown,

635
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,660
I should wear a better makeup.

636
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:19,260
Today,

637
00:30:19,260 --> 00:30:20,540
Qiuhe gave me a light makeup.

638
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:21,820
Later,

639
00:30:21,820 --> 00:30:23,380
I’m going to put up more.

640
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:26,780
His Majesty prefers guiding technique in combing.

641
00:30:27,820 --> 00:30:30,060
Because it massages the scalp

642
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:31,780
and regulates meridians,

643
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:33,980
to strengthen his body.

644
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:35,740
On the seventh day of July,

645
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:37,420
His Majesty wants to pick out

646
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:39,580
a combing maid who is good at guiding technique.

647
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:42,220
Different hairstyles and crowns

648
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:43,820
are also what a combing maid

649
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,100
should do.

650
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:49,260
But that’s not what His Majesty cares for most.

651
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:53,620
How do you think

652
00:30:54,980 --> 00:30:56,100
His Majesty

653
00:30:56,740 --> 00:30:58,220
can tell who does a better job

654
00:30:58,220 --> 00:31:00,540
in guiding technique?

655
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:02,460
Lately,

656
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:04,180
when Maid Dong combs your hair,

657
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:06,220
she mostly regulates your meridians.

658
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:08,700
She makes you simple hairstyles

659
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:10,500
without a crown

660
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:12,740
and only gives you a light makeup

661
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:15,500
so that His Majesty could see

662
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:18,140
your fresh complexion.

663
00:31:18,940 --> 00:31:20,100
It’s wise of His Majesty.

664
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:21,380
He will certainly know

665
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:22,660
Maid Dong is good at

666
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:24,060
the guiding technique.

667
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:37,580
Your Majesty.

668
00:31:38,500 --> 00:31:39,420
It’s done.

669
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:51,820
You’re having more complicated work,

670
00:31:52,740 --> 00:31:53,900
but limited strength.

671
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:56,580
With so many missions,

672
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:58,700
you’re sometimes not considerate enough.

673
00:32:00,660 --> 00:32:01,420
How about this?

674
00:32:03,100 --> 00:32:05,100
From next month, Yang Huaimin will help you.

675
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:07,660
He’s older than you,

676
00:32:08,140 --> 00:32:10,140
more experienced than you,

677
00:32:10,380 --> 00:32:11,580
and superior to you.

678
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:15,020
But you’ve worked for Imperial Security Agency

679
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,860
since you were twelve or thirteen.

680
00:32:17,340 --> 00:32:18,140
You’re more familiar.

681
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,660
In Imperial Security Agency,

682
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,420
you two will work together,

683
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,020
and communicate with each other

684
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:27,220
at the same level,

685
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:29,540
and report to Ren Shouzhong.

686
00:32:32,100 --> 00:32:32,940
I used to

687
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:36,380
give you orders personally.

688
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:38,940
It was against the rule.

689
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:40,660
I was wrong.

690
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:43,780
I won’t do that

691
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:47,620
ever again.

692
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:05,300
Maoze.

693
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,100
Here.

694
00:33:22,420 --> 00:33:23,180
Nothing.

695
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:35,780
Go ahead.

696
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:53,860
Master.

697
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:57,300
Going back!

698
00:34:13,820 --> 00:34:18,340
= The Seventh Day of July =

699
00:34:55,500 --> 00:34:56,300
Huirou.

700
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:58,540
What makes you so interested?

701
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,060
Everything.

702
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:02,340
It’s the first time you take me out, father.

703
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:04,780
I haven’t seen any before.

704
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:07,020
Don’t you like those in the palace?

705
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:09,740
The best things have been sent to our palace

706
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:11,660
from every quarter.

707
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:13,140
Really?

708
00:35:13,460 --> 00:35:15,940
Zongshi, Taotao,

709
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:18,460
Ruolan and Ruozhu told me

710
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,580
the fair of Great Xiangguo Temple,

711
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:23,700
the stationery store, the embroidery workshop

712
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:26,900
and the furniture store on the street

713
00:35:27,140 --> 00:35:28,580
were great fun.

714
00:35:30,540 --> 00:35:32,420
Things in the palace are more elaborate.

715
00:35:33,740 --> 00:35:36,060
When you grow up and get married,

716
00:35:36,500 --> 00:35:38,500
you can also go out and see the town.

717
00:35:39,660 --> 00:35:41,860
Can I often come back

718
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:43,980
to see you, Her Highness and my mother?

719
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:47,940
Sure.

720
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:49,540
You’re my daughter.

721
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:52,100
The palace will always be your home.

722
00:35:53,780 --> 00:35:54,620
Father.

723
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:57,820
Why can’t a eunuch

724
00:35:58,180 --> 00:36:00,940
take the imperial exam, be the principle graduate

725
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:02,700
or work as an official?

726
00:36:06,580 --> 00:36:09,220
This is a rule

727
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,180
that was made long long ago.

728
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:13,300
Over thousands of years,

729
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:15,620
it’s adopted by all dynasties.

730
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:19,260
Is it right

731
00:36:19,260 --> 00:36:20,020
and can’t be changed

732
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:21,420
only because it’s adopted by all dynasties?

733
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:24,860
People are always used to

734
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:26,380
such old rules,

735
00:36:26,380 --> 00:36:27,820
whether right or wrong.

736
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:31,580
They can hardly change.

737
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:34,060
Can’t we change it

738
00:36:34,460 --> 00:36:35,620
even when the Emperor finds it wrong?

739
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:37,980
Everyone listens to the Emperor.

740
00:37:12,580 --> 00:37:13,740
You’re wearing a nice crown.

741
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:16,540
Cai’er made it for me.

742
00:37:17,180 --> 00:37:17,940
Come.

743
00:37:21,140 --> 00:37:24,460
= Gu Cai’er =

744
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:27,540
Without any gems,

745
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:29,460
the crown still looks ornate.

746
00:37:30,060 --> 00:37:30,860
Well done.

747
00:37:32,140 --> 00:37:32,980
Thank you, Your Majesty.

748
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,220
How old are you?

749
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:37,260
When did you come to the palace?

750
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:39,540
I’m 19 years old.

751
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:40,780
It’s been five years.

752
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:43,780
Can you do the guiding technique?

753
00:37:44,620 --> 00:37:45,660
I’ve been learning the guiding technique

754
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:46,860
from my master.

755
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:48,300
In the past two years,

756
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,420
I’ve used it

757
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:51,180
to comb Madam Yu’s hair.

758
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:54,460
Good.

759
00:37:54,820 --> 00:37:56,100
Sit with her for the moment.

760
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:19,860
Greetings, Your Majesty.

761
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:21,100
Greetings, Your Highness.

762
00:38:24,900 --> 00:38:26,540
What a nice hairstyle!

763
00:38:27,620 --> 00:38:28,900
You look much better.

764
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:32,220
Looks like the young you

765
00:38:32,620 --> 00:38:33,580
who followed me

766
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:34,860
and called me brother.

767
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,380
Your Highness.

768
00:38:36,700 --> 00:38:38,860
Why did mother call father like that?

769
00:38:40,340 --> 00:38:42,140
Because she grew up

770
00:38:42,180 --> 00:38:43,460
- with your father. - The hairstyle

771
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:45,260
- Then why doesn’t she - was made by

772
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:47,100
- call father like that now? - the new maid?

773
00:38:47,660 --> 00:38:48,940
- I like that. - She did a really good job.

774
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,540
- Because your father is the Emperor.
- She’s very good at

775
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:52,386
combing with guiding technique.

776
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:54,260
- Your mother married him.
- After she combs my hair every day,

777
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:55,700
- She must obey the rules.
- I feel more energetic.

778
00:38:57,940 --> 00:38:59,580
That’s why I think it’s boring to stay here.

779
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:09,260
Where are you from?

780
00:39:09,980 --> 00:39:10,980
For your information,

781
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,260
I come from Yulin.

782
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,420
What does your family do?

783
00:39:15,780 --> 00:39:17,420
My family ran a shop of herbs and perfumes.

784
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:19,860
My father and grandfather had medical skills.

785
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:21,780
They saw patients in the shop.

786
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:25,500
Then why did you come to the palace?

787
00:39:27,060 --> 00:39:29,060
The border market was closed in recent years.

788
00:39:29,420 --> 00:39:31,500
Failing to get some important ingredients,

789
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:34,180
we failed to make our ancestral perfumes.

790
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:35,940
After the Sanchuankou War,

791
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:37,580
Yan’an was in urgent need of military physicians.

792
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:39,260
My father and grandfather

793
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:40,740
were recruited.

794
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:44,900
Yan’an?

795
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:47,580
1039 A.D.?

796
00:39:51,980 --> 00:39:53,260
Who took you to the palace?

797
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:55,540
It was

798
00:39:56,980 --> 00:39:58,500
the manager of Imperial Office Bureau,

799
00:39:58,580 --> 00:39:59,700
Mr. Zhang Maoze.

800
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:09,860
Oh, Maoze took you

801
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:11,260
back to the palace.

802
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:12,860
That explains.

803
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:16,380
You combed the hair for Her Highness, didn’t you?

804
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:19,900
That hairstyle looked different, too.

805
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:22,220
Be seated.

806
00:40:24,100 --> 00:40:25,980
Qiuhe, you’re young, but so capable.

807
00:40:26,420 --> 00:40:27,460
You’re indeed a good girl.

808
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:53,700
= Yang Huaimin =

809
00:40:55,220 --> 00:40:55,940
What?

810
00:40:56,420 --> 00:40:58,100
= Xu Lantiao =
You’re free today?

811
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:02,980
Nearly half people went to the Court of Rarity.

812
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:04,500
Even if you work hard here,

813
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:05,700
no one will see you.

814
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,380
Silly girl.

815
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:11,060
She’s too busy to hate you.

816
00:41:11,420 --> 00:41:12,860
And you have me.

817
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:13,820
You don’t need to

818
00:41:13,820 --> 00:41:15,860
flatter her in such a pitiful way.

819
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:18,580
But I’m scared.

820
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:21,180
After all, what she says

821
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,060
carries more weight in front of His Majesty,

822
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,180
even than the Empress.

823
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:30,780
She’s an idiot.

824
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:35,020
His Majesty spoils her over trifles.

825
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:36,980
But more than the Empress?

826
00:41:38,820 --> 00:41:40,460
I’m afraid

827
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:42,180
no one else thinks so, except her.

828
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:43,620
Even Chief Xia

829
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:44,140
only took her

830
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:45,460
as a messenger

831
00:41:45,460 --> 00:41:46,620
for delivering news.

832
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,780
Unless she gives birth to a son.

833
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,900
Even though, she may not use it wisely.

834
00:42:01,580 --> 00:42:04,340
You’re beautiful and clever.

835
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:06,140
Much better than her.

836
00:42:07,300 --> 00:42:09,140
Look what you’ve done.

837
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:11,940
When she finally attracted His Majesty

838
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:13,020
and stayed with him,

839
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:15,140
I was thinking how to defend you.

840
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:17,820
I thought I had to send you away

841
00:42:17,820 --> 00:42:19,180
and couldn’t meet you again.

842
00:42:20,180 --> 00:42:21,820
But you were so clever.

843
00:42:22,100 --> 00:42:24,380
You knew exactly what she wanted,

844
00:42:24,860 --> 00:42:27,180
and easily made Madam Miao take the blame

845
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:28,380
for tricking her.

846
00:42:28,820 --> 00:42:31,020
You also made her suspect every day

847
00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:32,780
and she nearly had an abortion of

848
00:42:32,780 --> 00:42:33,940
her own baby.

849
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:38,460
What a genius you are!

850
00:42:50,420 --> 00:43:00,100
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

851
00:43:01,420 --> 00:43:09,780
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

852
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:17,340
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

853
00:43:18,300 --> 00:43:22,460
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

854
00:43:23,900 --> 00:43:29,380
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

855
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:34,180
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

856
00:43:37,860 --> 00:43:43,500
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

857
00:43:43,500 --> 00:43:48,380
